{"tid":1042873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國駐加拿大使館：展開引渡聆訊程序是政治迫害","createTime":"2019-03-01T23:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T03:24:18.000Z","uid":23993,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9cef15316c6fbe9142960182958b202d604129","tid":1042873,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T23:40:45.000Z","msg":"加拿大授權法院對中國電訊商華為副董事長孟晚舟，展開引渡聆訊程序。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐加拿大大使館發表聲明，表示對加拿大司法部就孟晚舟案簽發授權進行令，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n聲明認為，孟晚舟案不是一宗簡單的司法案件，而是對一家中國高科技企業的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政治迫害</span></strong></span>，後來的事態發展證明了這一點，雖然加方標榜「法治原則」、「司法獨立」，但並不能掩蓋其在孟晚舟案上犯下的錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，如果加方真的遵循法治原則、司法獨立，就應該按照加拿大引渡法的有關條款，拒絕美方引渡請求，立即釋放孟晚舟，加拿大法庭的最終審理結果，將是對加方是否堅持司法獨立的試金石，中方將拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445616-20190302.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445616-20190302.htm&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=ab00e01d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445616-20190302.htm&h=6e5df60e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445616-20190302.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd4c41d2f4c7e89b41f221e8edaeb978e3080d6","tid":1042873,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T23:49:04.000Z","msg":"大使館干預加拿大司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b981ad2fd8d8b7e498b29cbc1b38749d2be2f3f","tid":1042873,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"只有人地害自己<br />\n從來冇自己害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beff9da086bf9053be3091e8b659a68b1ec45afa","tid":1042873,"uid":9031,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T01:34:00.000Z","msg":"中國無資格對加拿大內政說三道四"},{"pid":"d448ff7feea8076301741ddb85074887b3cc8989","tid":1042873,"uid":47259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"支那上次聆訊之後拉咗果三件加佬宜家乜環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f160fa8da8338e10621dc47b7e0be6a530e2525c","tid":1042873,"uid":65738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"別在其國事務上說三道四"},{"pid":"daefbf62f91f98e33ed888c9e1f5f9dbe1aee591","tid":1042873,"uid":115608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"你係冇做過，怕咩俾人審？<br />\n<br />\n人地美國司法點似得你冇罪著都會變有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5eda5fb712d414594917b3edbdfdffd9aefdb86","tid":1042873,"uid":3873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"學吳秋北話齋，滾蛋"},{"pid":"7d9b56f0ba72562cc37983d12b421a7f8cca6494","tid":1042873,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28f27b55120c38a12cee30509b459d3d316532a","tid":1042873,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"daefbf62f91f98e33ed888c9e1f5f9dbe1aee591","tid":1042873,"uid":115608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"你係冇做過，怕咩俾人審？<br />\n<br />\n人地美國司